overview: Bully is looking for the Vikings!Faxe, Tjure, Snorre, Ulme, Urobe and Gorm are the names of the "strong men" Michael "Bully" Herbig is looking for in his new casting show for a live-action adaptation of the cult children's series "Wickie". For the film adaptation, which is to be released in autumn 2009, only the six most talented men and those closest to the respective cartoon characters will be taken...
